# Cursed Japan ARPG — UI Wireframe Text Spec v1.0

> All screens are designed browser-first, mobile-responsive.
> React owns all screens listed here except the Battle Panel inner combat canvas (Phaser).
> Layout notation: [ELEMENT] = interactive component, {ELEMENT} = display only, | = column divider.

---

## Screen 1: World Map Screen

**Route:** `/map`
**Purpose:** Navigate the overworld, select nodes, view region info, access travel.

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  ⚔️  CURSED JAPAN          [🎒 Inventory]  [📖 Runes]  [🌿 Passive]  │  ← Top Nav Bar
│  Lv.12  ██████████░░  EXP 4,200 / 6,000   {Gold: 3,200}             │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                                     │
│   REGION: EDO STREETS         [◀ Chapter 1]  [Chapter 2 🔒 ▶]      │  ← Chapter Scroll
│                                                                     │
│   ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐       │
│   │                   OVERWORLD MAP CANVAS                  │       │
│   │                                                         │       │
│   │    [●] Market Camp ──── [●] River Shrine ──── [⚑] Oni  │       │  ← Region Nodes
│   │         EnemyCamp            Shrine              Boss   │       │
│   │           Lv.8                 ★                Lv.15  │       │
│   │            │                                     ▲     │       │
│   │    [●] Back Alley ───────── [◆] Ronin Den ───────┘     │       │
│   │       EnemyCamp               Miniboss                  │       │
│   │         Lv.10                  Lv.12                    │       │
│   │                                                         │       │
│   │   [🔒 Dark Forest — Recommended Lv.20+]                 │       │  ← Locked region (visible)
│   └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘       │
│                                                                     │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  SELECTED NODE: Market Camp                                         │  ← Node Info Panel
│  Type: Enemy Camp  |  Enemies: Ronin, City Guard  |  Power: ~100    │
│  Drops: Common Runes, Iron Ore, Low-tier Gear                       │
│                                                                     │
│  [⚔️ Fight (Auto)]    [🏃 Idle Farm Here]    [📋 Boss Info]          │  ← Action Buttons
│                                                                     │
│  Idle Status: ⏸ Not Farming  →  [▶ Start Idle Farm]                │  ← Idle Toggle
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Node states
| State | Visual | Action |
|---|---|---|
| Undiscovered | Greyed, fog icon | Auto-reveals when adjacent node cleared |
| Discovered | Default node icon | Can navigate, shows basic info |
| Cleared (first) | Checkmark on node | Idle farming available |
| Active idle | Pulsing ring animation | Stop button shown |
| Boss arena | Skull/red icon | Shows boss detail button |
| Shrine | Torii gate icon | Teleport, heal, respawn point |

### Notes for developer
- Map canvas: SVG or Phaser lightweight scene; nodes as positioned buttons with connector lines.
- Selected node panel slides up from bottom on mobile.
- Chapter scroll only shows unlocked chapters; locked chapters show region name with 🔒 + recommended level.
- Idle farm state persists in `useMapStore`; icon pulses when idle is active.

