## Screen 2: Battle Panel (Battle Screen)

**Route:** `/battle`
**Purpose:** Active combat — auto for normal enemies, manual option for bosses.
**Layout:** React HUD wrapping a Phaser canvas in center.

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  ◀ Map     MARKET CAMP — Wave 3/5            ⚡ 1x  [2x]  [4x]     │  ← Battle Header
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                                     │
│  ┌─── PLAYER HUD (React) ──────────────────────────────────────┐   │
│  │  HP  ████████████████░░░  820 / 1000                        │   │
│  │  RS  ████████░░░░░░░░░░░   48 / 100  (Resource)             │   │
│  │  BA  ░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░    0 / 200  (Barrier — inactive)   │   │
│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │
│                                                                     │
│  ┌─── PHASER COMBAT CANVAS ─────────────────────────────────────┐   │
│  │                                                              │   │
│  │        [Player Sprite]          [Enemy 1] [Enemy 2]         │   │
│  │           ↓ slash                  -248!    -112!           │   │
│  │                                                              │   │
│  │  Floating damage numbers, hit FX, death dissolve effects    │   │
│  │                                                              │   │
│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │
│                                                                     │
│  ┌─── ENEMY HUD (React, updates via EventBus) ──────────────────┐   │
│  │  Ronin        HP ██████░░░  360/500    🩸 Bleed (3t)         │   │
│  │  City Guard   HP ██████████ 500/500                          │   │
│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │
│                                                                     │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  SKILL BAR                                                          │  ← Skill Slots (React)
│                                                                     │
│  ┌──────────┐  ┌──────────┐  ┌──────────┐  ┌──────────┐           │
│  │[1] SLASH │  │[2] STORM │  │[3] GUARD │  │[4] BURST │           │
│  │  ████░░  │  │  ░░░░░░  │  │ READY ✓  │  │ ░░░░░░░░ │           │
│  │  2.1s CD │  │  5.0s CD │  │  0.0s CD │  │  12s CD  │           │
│  └──────────┘  └──────────┘  └──────────┘  └──────────┘           │
│                                                                     │
│  [⏸ Pause Auto]    [🛡 Manual Mode]    [🏃 Retreat]                │  ← Control Buttons
│                                                                     │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  COMBAT LOG (scrollable, last 5 lines)                              │
│  > Shadow Slash hit Ronin for 248 (Physical, Bleed applied)         │
│  > Storm Step hit City Guard for 112 (Lightning)                    │
│  > Ronin attacked you for 45 (blocked by Barrier)                   │
│  > Ronin DIED — dropped: Iron Shard x2                              │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Boss battle variant
When `bossId` is present, the layout adds:

```
│  ┌─── BOSS HUD ───────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │
│  │  ONI WAR GENERAL    Phase 1/2                                  │  │
│  │  HP  ████████████████████░░░░  6,800 / 8,000                  │  │
│  │  ⚠️  GROUND SMASH incoming in 3 ticks... [GUARD NOW]          │  │  ← Telegraph warning
│  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │
```

### Notes for developer
- Skill slot cooldown bar fills with CSS animation; React re-renders on store tick.
- Phaser handles all sprite movement and FX; React handles all HUD overlays.
- Combat log lines stored in local state (last 20 lines), not in global store.
- `[Manual Mode]` button disables auto-skill firing; player presses skill buttons manually.
- Speed buttons (1x / 2x / 4x) adjust `battleSpeed` in settings store; Phaser scene reads this to adjust tick interval.

