## Screen 3: Result / Loot Screen

**Route:** `/result` (shown as modal overlay after battle ends)
**Purpose:** Show EXP gained, loot dropped, crafting materials earned.

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                         BATTLE COMPLETE                             │
│                   Market Camp — Wave 5/5 ✓                         │
├──────────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────┤
│   EXP GAINED                 │   LOOT DROPPED                      │
│                              │                                      │
│   +1,240 EXP                 │  ┌─────────────────────────────┐   │
│   ████████████████░░  84%    │  │ [Magic] Iron Wakizashi      │   │  ← Item card
│   Lv.12 → 13 in 2 more runs │  │  +14% Attack Speed          │   │
│                              │  │  +8 Flat Damage             │   │  ← Affixes preview
│   MATERIALS                  │  │  [Equip?]  [Stash]  [Sell]  │   │
│   Iron Shard    x 6          │  └─────────────────────────────┘   │
│   Coarse Cloth  x 3          │                                      │
│   Fire Essence  x 1          │  ┌─────────────────────────────┐   │
│                              │  │ [Common] Link Rune: Added   │   │
│   GOLD                       │  │         Fire Damage         │   │
│   + 340 Gold                 │  │  Adds 10–18 Fire dmg to     │   │
│                              │  │  linked Strike skills       │   │
│                              │  │  [Add to Rune Bag]  [Sell]  │   │
│                              │  └─────────────────────────────┘   │
│                              │                                      │
│                              │  + 2 more items... [View All]       │
├──────────────────────────────┴──────────────────────────────────────┤
│  [⚔️ Fight Again]       [🗺 Back to Map]       [🎒 Open Inventory]   │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Item card states on result screen
| State | Displayed as |
|---|---|
| Better than equipped | Green border + "UPGRADE ↑" badge |
| Same slot, worse | Default |
| New rune (not owned) | Gold border + "NEW" badge |
| Duplicate rune | Grey border + "DUPLICATE" |

### Notes for developer
- Each item card uses `<ItemCard />` component.
- [Equip?] immediately opens comparison against currently equipped item.
- [Stash] adds to inventory; [Sell] converts to gold using item base sell value.
- EXP bar animates fill over 1.5s using CSS transition.

