```

### Rune tooltip (on hover/tap)
```
┌────────────────────────────────┐
│  🔥 Infused Flame  [Link Rune] │
│  ─────────────────────────── │
│  Adds 10–18 Fire damage to    │
│  linked Strike skills.        │
│  Modifies: Strike tag only    │
│  Drop source: Fire Kami Boss  │
│                  Volcano Pass │
└────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Notes for developer
- Skill slots should validate weapon compatibility via `engine/runes/runeValidator.ts` before accepting a drag.
- Weapon-exclusive rune shows ⚔️ icon + weapon family name. If incompatible weapon equipped, slot shows ⚠️ warning.
- Link slot count comes from `SkillRune.maxSupportLinks`.
- Filter options: All / Skill / Link / By Element (Fire, Cold, etc.).

