## Screen 5: Passive Web Screen

**Route:** `/passive`
**Purpose:** Allocate passive points into a spider-web-style node graph.

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  ◀ Back       PASSIVE WEB              Points: 8 available / 24 used│
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                                     │
│   [Search node...]                      [Reset All — Cost: 1000g]  │
│                                                                     │
│  ┌──────────────────── SVG / Canvas Web ───────────────────────┐   │
│  │                                                             │   │
│  │      ○──○──○                                                │   │  ← stat nodes
│  │      │     │                                                │   │
│  │   ◉──◉     ◉──◉──◉                                          │   │  ← ◉ = allocated
│  │      │         │                                            │   │
│  │      ◆─────────◆                                            │   │  ← ◆ = keystone
│  │      │         │                                            │   │
│  │   ○──○      ○──○──○                                         │   │
│  │                │                                            │   │
│  │             [PLAYER]                                        │   │  ← Center start node
│  │                │                                            │   │
│  │   ○──○──○   ○──○──○                                         │   │
│  │      │         │                                            │   │
│  │      ◆         ◆                                            │   │
│  │   Blade Fury  Iron Skin                                     │   │
│  │  (Keystone)  (Keystone)                                     │   │
│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │
│                                                                     │
│  SELECTED NODE:  +8 Strength  (StatNode)                           │  ← Selected info panel
│  Effect: +8 Strength (→ +4 Armor, +2 Base Damage)                  │
│  Cost: 1 point  |  Requires: Path connected from start             │
│  [Allocate — 1pt]    [Deallocate]                                   │
│                                                                     │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Node visual legend
```
○   = Unallocated stat node (reachable)
◉   = Allocated stat node
◆   = Keystone node (large, has text label)
◈   = Notable node (medium-sized, named effect)
●   = Locked node (not yet reachable — path not connected)
```

### Notes for developer
- Web rendered as SVG with nodes as `<circle>` and edges as `<line>`.
- `PassiveWebScreen.tsx` reads `passiveNodes.json` for positions and connections.
- Allocation validates path connectivity (only nodes adjacent to allocated path are activatable).
- Keystone tooltip shows full effect text + warning if it changes playstyle significantly.
- Mobile: pinch-zoom and drag pan supported on SVG canvas.

