│                                      │  [Equip]  [Sell 340g] [Salvage]│
└──────────────────────────────────────┴──────────────────────────────┘
```

### Item rarity colors
| Grade | Color |
|---|---|
| Normal | White |
| Magic | Blue |
| Rare | Yellow |
| Legendary | Orange |
| Unique | Red-gold |
| Holy | Teal-white glow |

### Notes for developer
- Bag slots use CSS Grid (6 columns × 6 rows = 36 slots recommended).
- Clicking a bag item opens the detail panel on right (desktop) or bottom sheet (mobile).
- Compare button appears when hovering over a bag item that occupies an already-equipped slot — shows side-by-side stat diff with ▲/▼ indicators.
- [Sell All Junk] auto-sells all Normal grade items not locked.

