## Screen 8: Offline Summary Screen

**Route:** Modal on app load if offline time > 60 seconds
**Purpose:** Show what the player accrued while away; apply gains on dismiss.

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    🌙 WELCOME BACK                                  │
│               You were away for 4 hours 32 minutes                 │
├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│   Idle farming in:  Market Camp — Edo Streets                       │
│   Power Score: 340  |  Zone Level: 8  |  Rate: Normal              │
├──────────────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────┤
│   EXP GAINED                     │  MATERIALS GATHERED              │
│                                  │                                  │
│   +8,640 EXP                     │  Iron Shard       x 24           │
│   ▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓░░  Lv.14!   │  Coarse Cloth     x 12           │
│   Level Up: 12 → 14              │  Fire Essence     x  3           │
│   +2 Passive Points gained       │  Gold              + 1,280       │
│                                  │                                  │
│                                  │  Rune Dust        + 40           │
├──────────────────────────────────┴──────────────────────────────────┤
│  ℹ️  Rare runes and unique items are not gained through idle farming. │  ← Reminder
│     Defeat bosses manually for build-defining drops.                │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                  [✅ Collect & Continue]                             │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Notes for developer
- Gains calculated by `engine/progression/offlineAccrual.ts` on app load.
- Gains are NOT applied to store until player taps [Collect & Continue].
- If player levelled up multiple times, show all level-ups and total passive points.
- Cap displayed as info tooltip: "Max idle farming duration: 8 hours."
- If no idle farm was set before closing, show: "No idle zone selected. Visit the Map to set an idle farming spot."

---

## Screen 9: Boss Detail Screen (with Loot Table)

**Route:** `/boss/:bossId` or modal from Map node
**Purpose:** Show boss stats, phases, and full loot table before committing to fight.

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  ◀ Back       BOSS ENCOUNTER                                        │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                                     │
│   ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │
│   │  💀  ONI WAR GENERAL                          [BOSS]         │  │
│   │  Region: Dark Forest — Chapter 1 Boss                        │  │
│   │  Level: 15  |  Recommended Power: 400+                       │  │
│   │                                                              │  │
│   │  HP: 8,000  |  Phases: 2  |  First Kill Bonus: ✓            │  │
│   └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │
│                                                                     │
├───────────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────┤
│  BOSS ABILITIES               │  PHASES                            │
│                               │                                     │
│  ⚔️ Ground Smash              │  Phase 1 (100% → 50% HP)            │
│    Physical AoE, Telegraph    │  Standard attacks                   │
│    Warns 4 ticks before hit   │                                     │
│                               │  Phase 2 (50% → 0% HP)             │
│  🩸 War Slash                  │  Enrage: Atk Speed +40%            │
│    Physical, applies Bleed    │  Gains Bleed on all hits            │
│    Single target              │                                     │
│                               │                                     │
│  🔴 Oni Roar                  │  MY POWER: 340 / Recommended 400   │
│    Reduces player Armor 20%   │  ⚠️ Below recommended power.        │
│    for 5s                     │                                     │
├───────────────────────────────┴─────────────────────────────────────┤
│  FULL LOOT TABLE                                                    │
│                                                                     │
│  SIGNATURE DROPS (Boss exclusive)                                   │
│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────┬──────┬──────────────┐ │
│  │ Item                                     │ Rate │ Note         │ │
│  ├──────────────────────────────────────────┼──────┼──────────────┤ │
│  │ ⚔️ [Skill Rune] Shadow Slash             │  4%  │ Katana only  │ │
│  │ 💀 [Unique] Oni Mask Helmet              │  1%  │ Fixed stats  │ │
│  └──────────────────────────────────────────┴──────┴──────────────┘ │
│                                                                     │
│  SHARED DROPS (Regional pool)                                       │
│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────┬──────┬──────────────┐ │
│  │ Item                                     │ Rate │ Note         │ │
│  ├──────────────────────────────────────────┼──────┼──────────────┤ │
│  │ 🔵 [Link Rune] Added Bleed               │ 12%  │              │ │
│  │ 🟡 [Rare] Forest Armor (random affixes)  │  8%  │              │ │
│  │ 🔧 Dark Iron Shard (crafting material)   │ 45%  │ avg x3       │ │
│  │ 💰 Gold                                  │ 100% │ 800–1,400    │ │
│  └──────────────────────────────────────────┴──────┴──────────────┘ │
│                                                                     │
│  Kill count: 0  |  Total Shadow Slash drops: 0                     │  ← Personal tracking
│                                                                     │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  [⚔️ Fight Now — Manual]        [📋 Copy Boss Info]   [◀ Back]      │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Notes for developer
- Drop rates shown as published percentages directly from `bosses.json → signatureDrops` and `lootTableId`.
- Personal kill count tracked in `useChapterStore`.
- Power comparison uses `player.stats` vs `boss.recommendedPower` — show red warning if 20% below, yellow if 10% below.
- [Fight Now — Manual] transitions to `/battle` with `bossId` parameter set; always opens `BossScene.ts` in Phaser.

---

## Shared Component Reference

| Component | Used on screens | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `<ItemCard />` | Result, Inventory, Crafting | Item display with rarity border, affix list, action buttons |
| `<RuneCard />` | Rune Screen, Result | Rune display with element tag, tooltip |
| `<HPBar />` | Battle, Shrine, Character | Generic bar with color, current/max label |
| `<DamageTypeTag />` | Rune, Boss Detail | Colored pill badge: Fire, Cold, etc. |
| `<LootTable />` | Boss Detail | Drops table with rate column |
| `<RegionNode />` | World Map | SVG node button with state styling |
| `<PassiveNode />` | Passive Web | SVG circle with allocation state |
| `<ModalWrapper />` | Shrine, Offline, Loot | Full-screen overlay with backdrop |
| `<SkillSlot />` | Battle, Rune Screen | Skill icon + cooldown bar + link indicators |

---

## Mobile Layout Notes

All screens follow a single-column layout at viewport width < 768px:
- Top nav collapses to icon-only bar.
- Two-column panels (e.g., Inventory equipped + bag) stack vertically.
- Item details and node info open as bottom sheets (slide up from bottom, dismissable).
- Passive web uses touch pinch-zoom and drag pan on SVG canvas.
- Skill bar in battle uses large tap targets (min 48×48px per slot).
- Boss detail loot table scrolls horizontally on very small screens.

